# Comment Tests
Title: Comment Tests

## Dramatis Personae

ALICE - A speaker
BOB - Another speaker

## ACT I

### SCENE 1

// Line comment at the start of a section

ALICE
Hello, Bob.

// Line comment between dialogue lines

BOB
Hello, Alice.

/* Single-line block comment */

ALICE
How are you?

/*
Multi-line block comment.
This spans several lines.
It should all be ignored by the parser.
*/

BOB
I am well, thank you.

// Comment between scenes

### SCENE 2

// Comment at the start of a new scene

ALICE
Here we are in scene two.

/* Block comment
   between dialogue */

BOB
Indeed we are.

/*
A block comment
at the very end
of the play.
*/
